Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:18.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我梦到了一个非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:29.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人他  最终还是回到我身边了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:32.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还告诉了我一些重要的事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:37.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我不能就这样放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:41.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系  我一个人也可以努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:23.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天去外边走走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然走路还感觉有些辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我试着努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍稍休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到头来  还是要喝这个奇怪的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直和我们生活在一起的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:02:59.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像似曾相识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个吃闲饭的家伙走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}反正他要是找不到落脚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到时候就会返回这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也很辛苦的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:22.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直为了能让观铃留在神尾家而努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}终有一天会被带回橘他们家去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然和你一起生活但却无法照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因为如果喜欢上你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}分别的时候会很伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直以平静的心情等待着分别那天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过看来是没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经无法再欺骗自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}让你成为我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直跪在橘他们家门口求他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最后他们拗不过我就答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经决定了一个人努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}决定了不给其他人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:10.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎么了  观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原来你病得这么重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本以为只是热伤风而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}脚动不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去看医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一定可以治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  去找那个诊所的女大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一定会帮助我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去医院也是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我与往人一起找到了病因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天空中有另外一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人一直背负着些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因此我的身体才渐渐地不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}总是说些天方夜谭似的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像以往一样  我们继续互不干涉的生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}两个人各自活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我会一个人努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}说  说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是因为一直没关怀过你所以生我的气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:16.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不想去医院也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我会好好照顾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过两个人总比一个人好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们两个人一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吗  观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么样  好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下回会做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈做的饭总是很难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}孩子可也都是吃父母做的饭长大的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:00.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}难吃得都要哭出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}与我亲近的话  妈妈也会病倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃原来是在为这个苦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听我说  观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得病什么的我一点都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真要是得病了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我会感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:31.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不正说明我和观铃变得亲近了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:49.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剪多少合适
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交给妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:19.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  那就剪成观铃看上去最可爱的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈的皱纹变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要我把你剪成寸头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈很年轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:31.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}以前学校进行公开授课的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其他人的妈妈都是中年人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我自己很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时你回答错了问题哭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:44.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道答案却想出出风头就举手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那时妈妈大庭广众之下就来揍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谁让你说那个「嘎哦」来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是管教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多亏了您观铃才能长这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:57.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}成长了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个口头禅也不怎么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样倒是方便剪头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得和这边长短一致才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这回另一边又剪短了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}倒是剪得长短一致了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  变得非常短了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像变回小孩子了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}两个人一起重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  现在起重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呐  夏日祭快开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不说我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和妈妈一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那还用说 带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后  还想去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还没有和妈妈一起去过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小观铃想去的地方还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  想和妈妈一起做很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  做很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}让你的绘画日记写得满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我记着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永远不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么回事  观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了  还困吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘记了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是说好了和妈妈一起努力的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对啊  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈去了很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就是你的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}从今天开始重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在让你叫我妈妈那天到来以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就叫我晴子阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我借来了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  有了这个就能出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腿很疼走不动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才借了这个轮椅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  我来推着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一个人玩扑克牌更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  两个人一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到外边晒晒太阳多舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}还有很多很多有趣的事可以做哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}风在吹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}艳阳高照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了嗡嗡地叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吵得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我是你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:44.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也知道这孩子无法生活在人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才把她送来这个宁静的小镇中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过看来是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你还不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她已经是我家的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经得到了你父母的允许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我和你姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觉得麻烦的时候送到我这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想起来时又要带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾家就是这样方便的地方吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不能眼睁睁地看着在你身边生病的她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要在我面前讲普通话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}听得我好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  嚷嚷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨… 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直叫我妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}来  向晴子阿姨道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快  说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:39.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要带走观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直是孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是谁的责任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不正是我们的责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我才决定要一直陪在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:56.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}难道因为我们之间的矛盾你就要带走她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我脑子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道这话该怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过有一点可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起你我更想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:12.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今后也想和晴子阿姨生活在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对  想和晴子阿姨继续生活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:21.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:23.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:24.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}给我三天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果三天后这孩子说不想和我在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也就没什么可说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你带走她我也毫无怨言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你了  敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天能让我们找回母女亲情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小观铃真的是非常喜欢恐龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个是「慈母龙」（Maiasaura peeblesorum ）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}代表慈祥的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿  还真像我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这个是「速龙（恐爪龙）」（Velociraptor）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}代表敏捷的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈  像敬介一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底谁才是小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过忍耐一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到了海边应该会更凉爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我亲手做的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那样的话便当不就白做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}里面有甜甜的炸鸡蛋哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:41.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是观铃点的菜哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们好好地玩一天吧
