Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:51.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…那我不管你了
