Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我们回去  观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其实我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:58.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我根本不适合做母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不适合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直以来做的这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:06.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了  抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  看我抓它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是专门抓知了的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抓知了的阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:23.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像你那样胆小的孩子很需要我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在这！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:32.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抓到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}这样就可以安心地玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:42.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那  阿姨就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨  可以留在这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已经没什么可奢求的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:13.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能和你在一起  哪怕只有一天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我所希望的仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天是和敬介约好的期限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那个呆子会再询问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:39.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你则会回答想和他一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}会说  不再想和我在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}虽然暑假还很长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但属于我俩的暑假就在今天结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:00.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.14,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.12,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.99,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}分别前想带这孩子去一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.23,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}观铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:20.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是海哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.61,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}为了我俩能一起来到海边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.26,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底花了多少年的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原本可以将这么美的景色看个够的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我俩一直以来到底在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.54,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:51.99,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很重的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起当初你抱她来时已经过了不少岁月了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.05,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她能长这么大也都是全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}对了  让他抱着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.72,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她很喜欢这个毛绒玩具的
