Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要是还闹个不停的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:13.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就让她喝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.24,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她最喜欢的果汁
