Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.82,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:46.45,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}之后  那两个人在夕阳下谈了很久
