Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:48.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是不错的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:51.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  那是个悲伤的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世界上最悲伤的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:59.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不过呢  这就是我梦的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.84,0:24:02.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今后我会留在妈妈身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直… 永远…


